title: Ep. 849 - Science Worship Leads To Death
description:
Australia attacks its own citizens for protesting lockdown measures, Afghan refugees attack children and women in Wisconsin, and a new study shows the staggering number of people the lockdowns will have killed in the United Kingdom.
